"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-showbiz-tv-radio-1930116-antiques-roadshow-olympic-gold-medal-bbc\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"AnAntiques Roadshowguest recalled how her Olympic swimming grandmother initially got into the sport, having been labelled a \\\"dunce\\\".\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Expert Adam Schoon met with a guest called Julia for filming of theBBCdaytime series who had a collection of swimming medals, including an Olympic gold from Paris 1924.\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 177, \"end\": 182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"score\": 0.9999996932640913, \"rank\": 3.0673507048887885e-07, \"text\": \"Julia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Swimming medals, swimming badges and a photograph, who is it?\\\"\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Schoon began.\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's my grandmother Lucy Morton, swimming, she started swimming when she was about aged 10,\\\" Julia explained.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucy_Morton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lucy Morton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucy_Morton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucy_Morton\"}, {\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"score\": 0.9999996932640913, \"rank\": 3.0673507048887885e-07, \"text\": \"Julia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What happened was her dad said 'you are too much of a dunce at school, you do not seem to be doing very well' and he decided 'let us try swimming.'\\\"\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When Schoon questioned if she had inherited the \\\"swimming DNA\\\", Julia joked that she could \\\"swim a length\\\", so enough \\\"to save my life\\\".\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 712, \"end\": 717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"score\": 0.9999996932640913, \"rank\": 3.0673507048887885e-07, \"text\": \"Julia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Back to her remarkable rise, because it's covered in gold medals,\\\" Schoon continued.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I noticed that there is a number of medallions around here which she would have won for, I presume, county races, national races.\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's setting world records.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All of these are 15-carat gold but of course, all these smaller medals build up to really this one here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The expert then pointed out the Olympic medal with the guest giving some backstory to how her grandmother went on to be crowned a champion.\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In 1923, they actually became very interested in her and they asked her to start swimming in preparation for the 1924 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She trained and she went to Paris in 1924.\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1452, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992546691, \"rank\": 7.452780668847485e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She wasn't expected to win or anything.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Unfortunately, some of the Americans had got some sort of bug from what I heard.\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She made the final race in breaststroke 200m and everyone was apparently cheering, she got to the end and she had a chaperone and the chaperone said 'You have won!'\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Pulled her out of the pool, put her bathrobe on.\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was actually the first female swimmer to win a gold medal in swimming for Great Britain.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1886, \"end\": 1899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9532801938089152, \"rank\": 0.048761250132106, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really proud of her.\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At that age, that time, females were not doing anything like that and to have actually swam at the age of 27, I think it was quite old back then.\\\"\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    Schoon remarked: \\\"Well you are right to be proud, she was an incredible woman.\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Back to the medal, it's got her name on the rim, it is the gold but it's made of silver, silver gilt.\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was designed in Paris by a man called Andre Rivaud, it was made in the Paris mint and there were only 304 made as far as I know.\\\"\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2527, \"end\": 2532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992546691, \"rank\": 7.452780668847485e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2582, \"end\": 2587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992546691, \"rank\": 7.452780668847485e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Julia shared that Morton went on to coach for the Olympic team and chaperoned other swimmers around the country, adding: \\\"She just loved it.\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2642, \"end\": 2647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"score\": 0.9999996932640913, \"rank\": 3.0673507048887885e-07, \"text\": \"Julia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\"}, {\"begin\": 2660, \"end\": 2666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenock_Morton_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.7134701287970823e-13, \"text\": \"Morton\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenock_Morton_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenock_Morton_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was her life.\\\"\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was then time for the expert to reveal his appraisal, stating: \\\"So when it comes to the valuation, Olympic medal, \\u00a315,000?\\\"\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clearly stunned by the news, the guest gave a wide smile as she asked: \\\"What?\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 3007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The one medal?\\\"\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BBCviewers could hear Julia panting as Schoon elaborated: \\\"Just for that.\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3047, \"end\": 3052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"score\": 0.9999996932640913, \"rank\": 3.0673507048887885e-07, \"text\": \"Julia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the fact you have got all these gold medals and more here, another \\u00a315,000.\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But altogether, it just adds up to the most extraordinary record of the most incredible woman.\\\"\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3276, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Antiques Roadshow is available to watch on BBC One and BBC iPlayer.\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3278, \"end\": 3295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antiques_Roadshow\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0646749524563072e-36, \"text\": \"Antiques Roadshow\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antiques_Roadshow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antiques_Roadshow\"}, {\"begin\": 3321, \"end\": 3328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.8503234112993e-20, \"text\": \"BBC One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\"}, {\"begin\": 3333, \"end\": 3336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9957386403810023, \"rank\": 0.002859315447682337, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 3337, \"end\": 3344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iPlayer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3484, \"end\": 3497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.745329327625658e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3533, \"end\": 3546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.745329327625658e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"